OL,5, The Transport Secretary Grant Shapps   
OL,6, has described calls for him to         
OL,7, intervene to settle the ongoing dispute
OL,8, between the RMT transport union and    
OL,9, rail employers as a "red herring" and a
OL,10, "stunt".                               
OL,12,FBut he said outdated practices "had to 
OL,13,Fend" for a resolution to be possible.  
OL,15,FIn an interview with the BBC, Mr Shapps
OL,16,Facknowledged that he and the Treasury  
OL,17,Fhad "set an overall mandate" which     
OL,18,Fdictated how much money was available, 
OL,19,Fand that he had final sign-off on what 
OL,20,Fwas agreed.                            
